channel.description:
[url=http://"http://www.dfdreamed.com/forums.php"][img]http://s2.postimage.org/avm701da1/DF_Dreamed_Banner_1.gif[/img] [/url]
Website: [url=http://"http://www.dfdreamed.com/forums.php"]http://www.dfdreamed.com[/url]
Owner: Dead Fury
What revision is DFDreamed?
[ul][li]317 Loading 634.[/li][/ul]
What is the XP rate of DFDreamed?
[ul][li]4x RuneScape[/li][/ul]
Is DFDreamed's currency inflated?
[ul][li]No, we use very low amounts of gold.[/li][/ul]
What skills are 100% like runescapes?
[ul][li]Mining[/li] [li]Smithing[/li] [li]Woodcutting[/li] [li]Firemaking[/li] [li]Fishing[/li] [li]Cooking[/li] [li]Prayer[/li] [li]Thieving[/li] [li]Fletching[/li] [li]Crafting[/li] [li]Slayer[/li] [li]Runecrafting[/li][/ul]
Dungeons:
[ul][li]100% working Taverly and Edgeville dungeons[/li] [li]working tolerance system[/li][/ul]
DF Dreamed's motto is raising the bar. It's our motto because we shoot for high quality updates. We are raising the bar for private servers. DF Dreamed is NOT a DONATE server. You CAN NOT donate for Strong items, Experience, or gold. We believe the free to play experience is what is important. DF Dreamed is NOT a VOTE server. The server does NOT revolve around voting. DF Dreamed is NOT run by STAFF. Moderators can't ban, mute, kick, or anything! Moderators are there to help out ONLY. The server has NO RULES, as we believe freedom is the answer to a successful rsps community.
Trailer: http://youtu.be/G5V4SLRozy8
Full World Map: [img]http://img802.imageshack.us/img802/9105/map1r.png[/img]
Custom Teleport System: [img]http://img41.imageshack.us/img41/9708/map2gm.png[/img]
Unique Combat System & Reputation: [img]http://img213.imageshack.us/img213/2853/combatrep.png[/img]
Custom spellbook & magic system: [img]http://img600.imageshack.us/img600/4248/91a141593e8c4283a659b69.png[/img] Working Skillcape emotes &amp;amp;amp;amp; Other emotes you have to unlock: [img]http://img547.imageshack.us/img547/593/shin125.png[/img][img]http://img16.imageshack.us/img16/6947/yeahto.png[/img] Resources: [img]http://img46.imageshack.us/img46/1577/936343028db841b791ca928.png[/img][img]http://i.imgur.com/Dro8s.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/5qilrPr.png[/img] [img]http://img837.imageshack.us/img837/7949/5f6ddbc22abc46c0882647f.png[/img]
Create multiple characters under one account! [img]http://img571.imageshack.us/img571/3879/339834df6c534e7e866386a.png[/img] [img]http://dfdreamed.com/img/clip0075.gif[/img] Working Highscores: [img]http://img843.imageshack.us/img843/1714/highse.png[/img] Small things: [img]http://i.imgur.com/pxL3ErL.png[/img]
